      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "BLUE FRANKY (2) boasts a strong record this course with three wins and four minors from eight tries. Was out of placings last time (30.01) at Wentworth Park in a Grade 5, finishing fourth and beaten 6 lengths. Looks a key chance on best form. GO FORWARD MEG (8) turned spotting a big start finishing fourth (23.09) last time in a Grade 5 at Maitland. Has ability and can measure up. CLUB DOZER (4) was never in contention last time after drifting back at Gosford, but prior to that won easily by 4.5 lengths at Wentworth Park (30.19) beating Paw Rex in a Grade 5 on March 7. Form from his last run is proving to be solid. Great chance to atone. TINY SNIFFY (3) can finish much closer after missing a cheque at this track last start.",
